Quarter: The fiscal quarter in which the HR training sessions were conducted, e.g., Q2 2025.
Training_Sessions_Conducted: The total number of HR training sessions conducted in the specified quarter.
Employee_Participation: The number of employees who participated in the HR training sessions during the specified quarter.
Compliance_Focus: The specific compliance topics covered during the HR training sessions, such as data protection regulations or security protocols.
Training_Impact_Score: A score evaluating the effectiveness of the HR training sessions in terms of employee readiness and compliance understanding, ranging from 0 to 10.
